Avusa Committee Says It Asked Capitau Group to Make Firm Bid by Next Month

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-08-11T07:42:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-11/avusa-committee-says-it-asked-capitau-group-to-make-firm-bid-by-next-month.html
Avusa Ltd. (AVU) ’s independent sub-
committee dealing with an expression of interest from investors
led by Capital Holdings Ltd. asked that a firm intention to make
an offer be delivered within two weeks of the end of a due-
diligence exercise that’s scheduled to be completed on or before
Sept. 7.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
